'''''Scimitar of Kelso''''' was an [[AA-9 Coruscant freighter/Legends|AA-9 Coruscant freighter]] that left [[Coruscant/Legends|Coruscant's]] [[Pad 132]] for [[Nar Shaddaa/Legends|Nar Shaddaa]] two weeks after the end of the [[Clone Wars/Legends|Clone Wars]]. [[Ch'ord Sy'fon]] told [[Sagoro Autem]] to board it, in an attempt to lure him to [[Anakin Skywalker/Legends|Darth Vader]].

